PersonalMission.Name: HT-8: With Guns Blazing
PersonalMission.Description: Remember, your armor is your key strength. Cause as much damage as possible while your opponents enjoy the non-penetration messages over and over again.
PersonalMission.Hint: As a heavy tank, you are the backbone of your team. Enemy heavy tanks are just as important. Take them on and try to destroy them first, or at least keep them busy for as long as possible.

Primary.Conditions: •  Cause 2,000 HP of damage to heavy tanks
